# SturdyEngine5 build requirements
# Info:
# - Configure from the repo root with the shared CMake presets.
# - Ninja is the supported generator because the project uses C++ modules.
# - Clang is the tested C++23 compiler path.
# Deps:
# - All platforms: CMake, Ninja, Clang, Vulkan SDK, Slang SDK.
# - Windows: MSBuild / Visual Studio Build Tools.
# - Linux: autogen/autotools.
# See docs/IDE_SETUP.md for the full setup notes.

# Version-control metadata
.lore/

# Architecture/design-doc scratch space (see plans/README.md) — working notes, not shipped docs.
/plans/

# Build directories
build/
out/

# Shared third-party source cache (STURDY_SHARED_DEPS_CACHE): git checkouts reused across all
# build/<arch>/<os>/<profile> trees so each configuration does not re-download dependencies.
/.cache/

# Upstream dependency licenses, copied in from each FetchContent source tree at build time
# (see cmake/SturdyLicenses.cmake). Regenerated content, not tracked.
/thirdparty/licenses/

# JetBrains CLion / IDE build trees and per-developer config.
# Shared .idea/ project files (runConfigurations/, vcs.xml) stay tracked; the
# per-developer ones are filtered by .idea/.gitignore. CLion's default out-of-source
# build dirs (used only if someone builds without the presets) are never shared.
/cmake-build-*/
# CMakeUserPresets.json holds a developer's own local presets; CMakePresets.json is
# generated by cmake/GeneratePresets.cmake from the axis lists in cmake/SturdyMatrix.cmake —
# every editor task that needs it (see cmake/IDEBuild.cmake, cmake/ClangdView.cmake) regenerates
# it first, so neither file belongs in version control.
/CMakeUserPresets.json
/CMakePresets.json

# Stale/local root compile database files. The View As tasks point clangd directly
# at build/<arch>/<os>/<profile>/compile_commands.json instead.
/compile_commands.json

# CMake generated files and directories
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/CMakeConfigureLog.yaml
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/install_manifest.txt
**/CTestTestfile.cmake
**/CPackConfig.cmake
**/CPackSourceConfig.cmake
**/Makefile
**/build.ninja
**/.ninja_deps
**/.ninja_log
**/Testing/

# CMake FetchContent and external dependency build trees
**/_deps/
**/*-build/
**/*-subbuild/
**/*-populate-prefix/

# Compiler and linker outputs
*.o
*.obj
*.a
*.lib
*.so
*.so.*
*.dylib
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.d
*.gcda
*.gcno
*.gcov

# Runtime dumps and logs
*.log
*.dmp
*.core
core.*
